Text: Happy birthday, Mary! Hope you have a great one:)
Happy 38 th birthday to you. All the best.
Thank you, Mary. We had a friend in town and went out to make some memories this weekend. 38 is going to be a good year. Thank you again.

Many good tidings for you both is my
Wish for you guys

Mary, I wanted to personally thank you for the kind hospitality and the gifts you and Dave gave out. 

You both continue to be a source of tremendous kindness and you give so much to bring everyone together. 

Thank you again. Have a great day

. Thanks for the note. I really appreciate this.  I m always worried we did not do enough. And people came later.  We did not get to talk to you guys.  We hope to see you all again soon. Love you both
